Usage: snapFPlanIO [-help] [-selected] [[-userGrid ] | [-toIoRow  [-overlapRowOnly ]]]

-help               # Prints out the command usage
-overlapRowOnly     # snap to overlapping row only. (bool, optional)
-selected           # selected objects (bool, optional)
-toIoRow            # snap I/O onto I/O rows (bool, optional)
-userGrid           # pin blockages (bool, optional)